#: src/buildings.c:33
msgid ""
"The Larn Revenue Service has ordered us to not do business with tax evaders. "
"They have also told us that you owe back taxes and, as we must comply with "
"the law, we cannot serve you at this time.\n"
"\n"
"So Sorry."
msgstr ""
"La Agencia Tributaria de Larn nos ha ordenado que no realicemos "
"transacciones comerciales con evasores fiscales. También nos han informado "
"de que usted tiene impuestos atrasados y, dado que debemos cumplir con la "
"ley, no podemos atenderle en este momento.\n"
"\n"
"Lo sentimos mucho."

#: src/buildings.c:81
msgid "First National Bank of Larn"
msgstr "Primer Banco Nacional de Larn"

#: src/buildings.c:82
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the First National Bank of Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenido al Primer Banco Nacional de Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:84
msgid ""
"Welcome to the 5th level branch office of the First National Bank of Larn.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Bienvenido a la sucursal del quinto nivel del Primer Banco Nacional de "
"Larn.\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:87
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The Larn Revenue Service has ordered that your account be frozen until all "
"levied taxes have been paid.  They have also told us that you owe %d gold in "
"taxes, and we must comply with them. We cannot serve you at this time. "
"Sorry.\n"
"\n"
"We suggest you go to the LRS office and pay your taxes."
msgstr ""
"La Hacienda de Larn ha ordenado congelar tu cuenta hasta que se abonen todos "
"los impuestos exigidos. También nos han comunicado que debes %d de oro en "
"impuestos, y debemos obedecer. No podemos atenderte en este momento. Lo "
"sentimos.\n"
"\n"
"Te sugerimos acudir a la oficina de Hacienda y pagar tus impuestos."

#: src/buildings.c:104
#, c-format
msgid "We have paid you an interest of %d gold since your last visit.\n"
msgstr "Te hemos abonado %d de oro en intereses desde tu última visita.\n"

#: src/buildings.c:108
#, c-format
msgid "The bank has paid you an interest of %d gold since your last visit."
msgstr "El banco te ha abonado %d de oro en intereses desde tu última visita."

#: src/buildings.c:131
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You have %d gold pieces in the bank.\n"
"You have %d gold pieces.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Tienes %d piezas de oro en el banco.\n"
"Llevas %d piezas de oro.\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:135
msgid "Your wish? "
msgstr "¿Qué deseas? "

#: src/buildings.c:138
msgid "`KEY`d`end`)eposit "
msgstr "`KEY`d`end`) ingresar "

#: src/buildings.c:141
msgid "`KEY`w`end`)ithdraw "
msgstr "`KEY`w`end`) retirar "

#: src/buildings.c:145
msgid "`KEY`s`end`)ell a gem"
msgstr "`KEY`s`end`) vender una gema"

#: src/buildings.c:160
msgid "How many gold pieces do you wish to deposit?"
msgstr "¿Cuántas piezas de oro quieres ingresar?"

#: src/buildings.c:167
#, c-format
msgid "You deposited %d gold."
msgstr "Has ingresado %d de oro."

#: src/buildings.c:174
msgid "You don't have that much."
msgstr "No tienes tanto."

#: src/buildings.c:183
msgid "How many gold pieces do you wish to withdraw?"
msgstr "¿Cuántas piezas de oro quieres retirar?"

#: src/buildings.c:194
#, c-format
msgid "You withdraw %d gold."
msgstr "Retiras %d de oro."

#: src/buildings.c:204
msgid "You don't have that much in the bank!"
msgstr "¡No tienes tanto en el banco!"

#: src/buildings.c:218 src/buildings.c:906
msgid "(`KEY`s`end`)ell"
msgstr "(`KEY`s`end`) vender"

#: src/buildings.c:219
msgid "Sell the currently selected gem."
msgstr "Vende la gema seleccionada."

#: src/buildings.c:227
msgid "Sell gems"
msgstr "Vender gemas"

#: src/buildings.c:256
msgid "DND store"
msgstr "Tienda DND"

#: src/buildings.c:257
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the Larn Thrift Shoppe.`end`\n"
"\n"
"We stock many items explorers find useful in their adventures. Feel free to "
"browse to your heart's content. Also be advised that if you break 'em, you "
"pay for 'em."
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenido al Bazar de Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Tenemos muchos artículos que los exploradores encuentran útiles en sus "
"aventuras. Curiosea cuanto quieras. Y ten presente: si lo rompes, lo pagas."

#: src/buildings.c:342
msgid "Your home"
msgstr "Tu casa"

#: src/buildings.c:344
#, c-format
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome home, %s.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Latest word from the doctor is not good. The diagnosis is confirmed as "
"dianthroritis. He guesses that your daughter has only %d mobuls left in this "
"world. It's up to you, %s, to find the only hope for your daughter, the very "
"rare potion of cure dianthroritis.  It is rumored that only deep in the "
"depths of the caves can this potion be found.\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenido a casa, %s.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Las últimas noticias del médico no son buenas. El diagnóstico se confirma: "
"diantroritis. Calcula que a tu hija solo le quedan %d móbulos en este mundo. "
"De ti depende, %s, encontrar la única esperanza para tu hija, la rarísima "
"poción de cura de la diantroritis. Se rumorea que solo en lo más profundo de "
"las cuevas puede hallarse esta poción.\n"

#: src/buildings.c:353
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Congratulations!`end` You found the potion of cure dianthroritis! "
"Frankly, No one thought you could do it. Boy! Did you surprise them!\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`¡Enhorabuena!`end` ¡Has encontrado la poción de cura de la "
"diantroritis! Francamente, nadie te creía capaz. ¡Menuda sorpresa se han "
"llevado!\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:357
msgid ""
"The doctor has the sad duty to inform you that your daughter died before "
"your return. There was nothing he could do without the potion.\n"
"\n"
"You didn't make it in time. Too bad..."
msgstr ""
"El médico tiene el triste deber de informarte de que tu hija murió antes de "
"tu regreso. Sin la poción, nada pudo hacer.\n"
"\n"
"No llegaste a tiempo. Una lástima..."

#: src/buildings.c:362
msgid ""
"The doctor is now administering the potion and, in a few moments, your "
"daughter should be well on her way to recovery.\n"
"\n"
"The potion is working! The doctor thinks that your daughter will recover in "
"a few days.\n"
"\n"
"Congratulations!"
msgstr ""
"El médico está administrando la poción y, en unos instantes, tu hija debería "
"estar camino de la recuperación.\n"
"\n"
"¡La poción funciona! El médico cree que tu hija se recuperará en unos días.\n"
"\n"
"¡Enhorabuena!"

#: src/buildings.c:380 src/player.c:1095
msgid "You saved your daughter!"
msgstr "¡Has salvado a tu hija!"

#: src/buildings.c:400 src/buildings.c:411
msgid "You were too late!"
msgstr "¡Llegaste demasiado tarde!"

#: src/buildings.c:435
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"You may\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"Puedes\n"

#: src/buildings.c:438
msgid "  `KEY`d`end`) Deposit something here\n"
msgstr "  `KEY`d`end`) dejar algo aquí\n"

#: src/buildings.c:442
msgid "  `KEY`t`end`) Take something with you\n"
msgstr "  `KEY`t`end`) llevarte algo\n"

#: src/buildings.c:461
msgid "(`KEY`d`end`)eposit"
msgstr "(`KEY`d`end`) depositar"

#: src/buildings.c:462
msgid "Deposit the selected item in your storage room at home."
msgstr "Deposita el objeto seleccionado en el trastero de tu casa."

#: src/buildings.c:486
msgid "(`KEY`t`end`)ake"
msgstr "(`KEY`t`end`) llevar"

#: src/buildings.c:487
msgid ""
"Take the selected item out of your storage room and put it into your pack."
msgstr "Saca el objeto seleccionado de tu trastero y mételo en tu mochila."

#: src/buildings.c:497
msgid "take (`KEY`a`end`)ll"
msgstr "(`KEY`a`end`) llevar todo"

#: src/buildings.c:498
msgid ""
"Take all items from your storage room. Only available when you can carry the "
"total weight."
msgstr ""
"Llévate todos los objetos de tu trastero. Solo disponible cuando puedes "
"cargar con el peso total."

#: src/buildings.c:527
msgid "Larn Revenue Service"
msgstr "Hacienda de Larn"

#: src/buildings.c:528
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Larn Revenue Service district office.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Bienvenido a la oficina del distrito de la Hacienda de Larn.\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:529
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You presently owe %d gold in taxes.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Actualmente debes %d de oro en impuestos.\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:530
msgid "You do not owe us any taxes."
msgstr "No nos debes ningún impuesto."

#: src/buildings.c:543
msgid "Do you want to pay your taxes?"
msgstr "¿Quieres pagar tus impuestos?"

#: src/buildings.c:550
msgid "You have paid your taxes."
msgstr "Has pagado tus impuestos."

#: src/buildings.c:554
msgid "You chose not to pay your taxes."
msgstr "Has decidido no pagar tus impuestos."

#: src/buildings.c:559
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, it seems that you cannot afford to pay your taxes at this "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Por desgracia, parece que ahora mismo no puedes permitirte pagar tus "
"impuestos."

#: src/buildings.c:585 src/buildings.c:601 src/buildings.c:606
#: src/buildings.c:624 src/buildings.c:635 src/buildings.c:651
#: src/buildings.c:662 src/buildings.c:821 src/buildings.c:852
#: src/buildings.c:863
msgid "School"
msgstr "Universidad"

#: src/buildings.c:585
msgid "To craft a scroll, the scribes must first be given a blank one."
msgstr ""
"Para elaborar un pergamino, antes hay que entregar a los escribas uno en "
"blanco."

#: src/buildings.c:591
msgid "Choose a scroll to inscribe"
msgstr "Elige un pergamino para inscribir"

#: src/buildings.c:597 src/buildings.c:606
msgid "Okay then."
msgstr "De acuerdo, pues."

#: src/buildings.c:602
msgid "Which incantation shall we bind in ink?"
msgstr "¿Qué encantamiento fijaremos con tinta?"

#: src/buildings.c:625
msgid ""
"Even the oldest scribes know nothing of a scroll like that. Alas, the scroll "
"must remain blank - for even the greatest scribes cannot write what does not "
"exist."
msgstr ""
"Ni los escribas más ancianos saben de un pergamino así. Por desgracia, el "
"pergamino deberá quedar en blanco: ni el mayor de los escribas puede "
"escribir lo que no existe."

#: src/buildings.c:635
msgid "A blank scroll, by definition, needs no scribe."
msgstr "Un pergamino en blanco, por definición, no necesita escriba."

#: src/buildings.c:645
#, c-format
msgid ""
"You do not possess the %d gold necessary to acquire the scroll of %s. For "
"now, the scribes shall keep their quills dry."
msgstr ""
"No posees los %d de oro necesarios para adquirir el pergamino %s. Por ahora, "
"los escribas mantendrán secas sus plumas."

#: src/buildings.c:657
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The crafting of a scroll of %s demands a fee of %d gold.\n"
"Would that be agreeable to you?"
msgstr ""
"La elaboración de un pergamino %s exige unos honorarios de %d de oro.\n"
"¿Te parece aceptable?"

#: src/buildings.c:683
#, c-format
msgid "waiting for the scribes to write a scroll of %s for you"
msgstr "esperando a que los escribas te escriban un pergamino %s"

#: src/buildings.c:687
#, c-format
msgid "The scribes have completed a scroll of %s on your behalf."
msgstr "Los escribas han terminado un pergamino %s para ti."

#: src/buildings.c:706
msgid "Fighters Training I"
msgstr "Adiestramiento de combate I"

#: src/buildings.c:706
msgid "You feel stronger!"
msgstr "¡Te sientes más fuerte!"

#: src/buildings.c:707
msgid "Fighters Training II"
msgstr "Adiestramiento de combate II"

#: src/buildings.c:707
msgid "You feel much stronger!"
msgstr "¡Te sientes mucho más fuerte!"

#: src/buildings.c:708
msgid "Introduction to Wizardry"
msgstr "Introducción a la magia"

#: src/buildings.c:708
msgid "The task before you now seems more attainable!"
msgstr "¡La tarea que te aguarda parece ahora más alcanzable!"

#: src/buildings.c:709
msgid "Applied Wizardry"
msgstr "Magia aplicada"

#: src/buildings.c:709
msgid "The task before you now seems very attainable!"
msgstr "¡La tarea que te aguarda parece ahora muy alcanzable!"

#: src/buildings.c:710
msgid "Faith for Today"
msgstr "Fe para el presente"

#: src/buildings.c:710
msgid "You now feel more confident that you can find the potion in time!"
msgstr "¡Ahora confías más en poder encontrar la poción a tiempo!"

#: src/buildings.c:711
msgid "Contemporary Dance"
msgstr "Danza contemporánea"

#: src/buildings.c:711
msgid "You feel like dancing!"
msgstr "¡Te dan ganas de bailar!"

#: src/buildings.c:712
msgid "History of Larn"
msgstr "Historia de Larn"

#: src/buildings.c:712
msgid ""
"Your instructor told you that the Eye of Larn is rumored to be guarded by an "
"invisible demon lord."
msgstr ""
"Tu instructor te ha contado que, según los rumores, el Ojo de Larn está "
"custodiado por un señor demoníaco invisible."

#: src/buildings.c:724
#, c-format
msgid "taking the course \"%s\""
msgstr "asistiendo al curso «%s»"

#: src/buildings.c:766
#, c-format
msgid "You successfully complete the course \"%s\". %s"
msgstr "Completas con éxito el curso «%s». %s"

#: src/buildings.c:773
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the College of Larn!`end`\n"
"\n"
"We offer the exciting opportunity of higher education to all inhabitants of "
"the caves. Here is a list of the class schedule:\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`¡Bienvenido a la Universidad de Larn!`end`\n"
"\n"
"Ofrecemos la apasionante oportunidad de una educación superior a todos los "
"habitantes de las cuevas. Este es el programa de clases:\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:778
#, c-format
msgid "Sorry, but this class has a prerequisite of \"%s\"."
msgstr "Lo sentimos, pero esta clase tiene como requisito previo «%s»."

#: src/buildings.c:803
#, c-format
msgid " `KEY`%c`end`) `EMPH`%-24s`end` - %2d mobuls, %4d gold\n"
msgstr " `KEY`%c`end`) `EMPH`%-24s`end` - %2d móbulos, %4d de oro\n"

#: src/buildings.c:809
#, c-format
msgid "    %-24s - attended\n"
msgstr "    %-24s - cursado\n"

#: src/buildings.c:814
msgid "Commission a scroll"
msgstr "Encargar un pergamino"

#: src/buildings.c:817
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Alternatively,\n"
" `KEY`%c`end`) %-24s - 10 mobuls\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Como alternativa,\n"
" `KEY`%c`end`) %-24s - 10 móbulos\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:850
#, c-format
msgid "You cannot afford the %d gold for the course."
msgstr "No puedes permitirte los %d de oro del curso."

#: src/buildings.c:882
msgid "Trade Post"
msgstr "Puesto comercial"

#: src/buildings.c:884
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the Larn Trading Post.`end`\n"
"\n"
"We buy items that explorers no longer find useful.\n"
"Since the condition of the items you bring in is not certain, and we incur "
"great expense in reconditioning the items, we usually pay only 20% of their "
"value were they to be new.\n"
"If the items are badly damaged, we will pay only 10% of their new value."
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenido al Puesto Comercial de Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Compramos objetos que los exploradores ya no encuentran útiles.\n"
"Como el estado de los objetos que traes es incierto y reacondicionarlos nos "
"supone grandes gastos, normalmente pagamos solo el 20% de lo que valdrían "
"nuevos.\n"
"Si los objetos están muy dañados, pagaremos solo el 10% de su valor como "
"nuevos."

#: src/buildings.c:907
msgid "Sell the selected item to the Trade Post."
msgstr "Vende el objeto seleccionado al puesto comercial."

#: src/buildings.c:916
msgid "(`KEY`i`end`)dentify"
msgstr "(`KEY`i`end`) identificar"

#: src/buildings.c:917
msgid "Have the Trade Post's experts identify your item."
msgstr "Deja que los expertos del puesto comercial identifiquen tu objeto."

#: src/buildings.c:925
msgid "(`KEY`r`end`)epair"
msgstr "(`KEY`r`end`) reparar"

#: src/buildings.c:926
msgid ""
"Have the Trade Post's experts revert any damage done to the selected item."
msgstr ""
"Deja que los expertos del puesto comercial reviertan los daños del objeto "
"seleccionado."

#: src/buildings.c:934
msgid "(`KEY`e`end`)quip"
msgstr "(`KEY`e`end`) equipar"

#: src/buildings.c:935 src/player.c:2613
msgid "Equip the selected item."
msgstr "Equipa el objeto seleccionado."

#: src/buildings.c:942
msgid "(`KEY`u`end`)nequip"
msgstr "(`KEY`u`end`) desequipar"

#: src/buildings.c:943 src/player.c:2637
msgid "Unequip the selected item."
msgstr "Desequipa el objeto seleccionado."

#: src/buildings.c:951
msgid "(`KEY`n`end`)ote"
msgstr "(`KEY`n`end`) anotar"

#: src/buildings.c:952
msgid "Add a note to the item."
msgstr "Añade una nota al objeto."

#: src/buildings.c:971
msgid "The Monastery of Larn"
msgstr "El monasterio de Larn"

#: src/buildings.c:973
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome, traveler, to the Monastery of Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Peace be upon you. The walls of the monastery offer respite to all who seek "
"it.\n"
"\n"
"Speak your need, and if it lies within our calling, it shall be granted... "
"for a fair offering. We tend the wounded and weary, and offer a small "
"selection of tools and provisions to aid those who walk the road of trials.\n"
"\n"
"Here you may\n"
"\n"
"  `KEY`a`end`) buy something\n"
"  `KEY`b`end`) ask for curse removal\n"
"  `KEY`c`end`) receive healing\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Bienvenido, viajero, al monasterio de Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"La paz sea contigo. Los muros del monasterio ofrecen descanso a todo aquel "
"que lo busca.\n"
"\n"
"Di lo que necesitas y, si está en nuestra mano, te será concedido... por una "
"ofrenda justa. Atendemos a los heridos y fatigados, y ofrecemos una pequeña "
"selección de útiles y provisiones para ayudar a quienes recorren el camino "
"de las pruebas.\n"
"\n"
"Aquí puedes\n"
"\n"
"  `KEY`a`end`) comprar algo\n"
"  `KEY`b`end`) pedir que se retire una maldición\n"
"  `KEY`c`end`) recibir curación\n"

#: src/buildings.c:984
msgid "Shall we proceed, then?"
msgstr "¿Procedemos, entonces?"

#: src/buildings.c:1004
msgid "poison"
msgstr "el envenenamiento"

